menu "Garden Door Controller"

    config GARDEN_DOOR_AUTO_LOCK_DELAY_S
        int "Auto-lock delay after unlock (seconds)"
        default 10
        range 1 300
        help
            Number of seconds after which the door automatically locks
            again following an unlock command. Set to a higher value if
            you need more time to walk through the gate.

    config GARDEN_DOOR_RELAY_PULSE_MS
        int "Relay pulse duration (milliseconds)"
        default 3000
        range 500 30000
        help
            How long the relay stays energised when the door is unlocked.
            This is the buzzer activation time.

endmenu
